<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HOLH IN KA CHIM KHO LO CH132</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh keimah a ka dawt ca, Vailamtahnak kha a huah cang; Keimah tlanh
 awkah dawtnak kha, Holh in ka chim kho lo.

[C1]
   Bawi Jesuh dawtnak a vel kha (dawtnak a vel kha) Ka hmurka in ka
   chim kho lo (ka chim kho lo) Amah a dawtnak a tam ca'h, Holh in ka chim
   kho lo.

[V2]
 Keimah ka lu nunter awkah, Ngaihchiat sifahnak kha a huah; Hling
 luchin an chinh luchin ah, Sifah ka chim kho lo.

[C2]
   Bawi Jesuh dawtnak a vel kha (dawtnak a vel kha) Ka hmurka in ka
   chim kho lo (ka chim kho lo) Amah a dawtnak a tam ca'h, Holh in ka chim
   kho lo.

[V3]
 Ka Bawipa hnangamnak ka hmuh, Pathian sinin a ka halpiak; Thisen sung
 in a ka tlanh cang, Holh in ka chim kho lo.

[C3]
   Bawi Jesuh dawtnak a vel kha (dawtnak a vel kha) Ka hmurka in ka
   chim kho lo (ka chim kho lo) Amah a dawtnak a tam ca'h, Holh in ka chim
   kho lo.

[V4]
 A ka naih tikah kaa lawm i, Dinhnak tha kha a ka pek ko; Ruahchannak a
 ka pekmi kha, Holh in ka chim cawk lo.

[C4]
   Bawi Jesuh dawtnak a vel kha (dawtnak a vel kha) Ka hmurka in ka
   chim kho lo (ka chim kho lo) Amah a dawtnak a tam ca'h, Holh in ka chim
   kho lo.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>132</hymn_number>
</song>